<div class="page-hero">
    <h1>About This Portal</h1>
    <p>Learn how the Student Service Portal works and who it's for.</p>
</div>

<div class="content-card">
    <h2>What is the Student Service Portal?</h2>
    <p>The Student Service Portal is an online system that lets JustAnother College students submit requests to the Student Services Office without having to visit in person or send an email. The goal is to make it easier to get help with things like replacing a lost student card or getting an official enrollment letter.</p>
    <p>All requests are reviewed by a member of the services team and responded to within the timeframe listed for each service type.</p>
</div>

<div class="content-card">
    <h2>Who Can Use It?</h2>
    <p>Any currently enrolled student at JustAnother College can submit a request. You'll need your student ID number in the format XXX-XXX-XXXX and a photo of your student card to verify your identity.</p>
</div>

<div class="content-card">
    <h2>How to Submit a Request</h2>
    <ol class="steps-list">
        <li>Go to the <a href="/request">Submit Request</a> page.</li>
        <li>Fill in your name, student ID, email, and program.</li>
        <li>Choose the service you need and how urgent your request is.</li>
        <li>Describe your situation in the text box.</li>
        <li>Upload a photo of your student card (JPG or PNG).</li>
        <li>Click Submit — you'll see a confirmation page with your request number and estimated response time.</li>
    </ol>
</div>

<div class="content-card">
    <h2>Contact Student Services</h2>
    <p>If you have questions that aren't covered by the portal, you can reach the Student Services Office directly:</p>
    <ul class="contact-list">
        <li>Email: <a href="mailto:services@justanother.edu">services@justanother.edu</a></li>
        <li>Phone: (416) 555-0192</li>
        <li>Office hours: Monday – Friday, 9:00 AM – 4:00 PM</li>
        <li>Location: Room 204, Administration Building</li>
    </ul>
</div>

